<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>SupaSpy</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/reset.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/main.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div id="wrapper">
    <div class="content-floor">
      <span class="content-door">
        <a href="/">s</a>
      </span>
      <div class="content-anteroom">
        <h1>
          upaspy
        </h1>
        <p>
          Hi, so you want to check if your friend has visited some concrete www pages?
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-floor content-floor-active">
      <span class="content-door">
      1
      </span>
      <div class="content-anteroom">
        <p>
          Type url addresses of these pages.
        </p>
        <p>
          Your email would be handy if you want to see results.
        </p>
      </div>
			<div class="content-sitting-room" id="content-1">
      <%= yield %>
			</div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-floor">
      <span class="content-door">
        2
      </span>
      <div class="content-anteroom">
        <p>
         A personalized supaspy link is generated for you.
        </p>
        <p>
         Your friend has to visit the link. 
         Use the supaspy sender or provide the link yourself.
        </p>
        <p>
         You will get results in your mailbox.
        </p>
      </div>
			<div class="content-sitting-room" id="content-2">
        <p>
          <a href="#" id="done" class="button">
            done<span class="ques">?</span><span class="excl">!</span>
            generate the link
          </a>
        </p>
			</div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-floor">
      <span class="content-door">
        *
      </span>
      <div class="content-anteroom">
        <p>
          Don't be afraid of your email, your friend email, the results or anything else.
        </p>
      </div>
			<div class="content-sitting-room">
        <p>
          Supaspy does <strong>NOT</strong>:<br/>
          - sell email addresses to viagra shops<br/>
          - share results with anyone but you<br/>
          - interest in IP addresses or cookies<br/>
          - install anything on your hdd<br/>
        </p>
			</div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-floor">
      <span class="content-door">
        @
      </span>
      <div class="content-anteroom">
        <p>
          Questions,  
          suggestions, 
          complaints,
          anything?
        </p>
      </div>
			<div class="content-sitting-room">
        supaspy@supaw.eu
			</div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-floor">
    </div>
  </div>

	<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/mootools/1.3.2/mootools-yui-compressed.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/urls.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/main.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/spy.js"></script>
</body>
